channel.title: Help needed on a 614 client!
channel.description: Where are the models located on a 614 client? I cant find them! i searched for them but nothing, i dont know if they are in a file called "models" or if the client has them. But if they have models, please tell me what the folder is called and where its located. THANKS!!!!

item.title: Help needed on a 614 client!
item.dc:creator: @naruto11230 naruto11230
item.description:
@naruto11230 wrote:

[quote=“badger41, post:4, topic:361717”][quote author=naruto11230 link=topic=457985.msg3351617#msg3351617 date=1285384509]

lol, the models are located in the cache, in the main file cache dat files and the idx files.

[/quote] I have a file called “.jagex_cache_32” but all thats in there is .dll files Im just after the dungoneering skillcape and emote models

download a cache extractor and use it on the 614 cache, it extracts models and other things.[/quote]is it called a UT cache extractor?
